title: Naruto - Fukashi no Aijou, Kashi no Koi (Doujinshi)
description:
Pairing: Naruto x Sasuke

Sasuke is approached by a mysterious figure promising him power if he captures Naruto, Konoha's current Hokage. As a trusted member of ANBU, the job should be easy for him, but does Sasuke have any intentions of betraying Naruto?
